<h4>Ding 4!</h4>
<p>
Congratulations…you've proven yourself to the guild and have been granted
permission to summon elementals! You're a full-fledged magician!&nbsp; But, before you rush off to summon Jobekn away from
his family, let me explain a little bit about pets. In this level, you become a
magician. There is more to learn at level 4 than any other level. Historical
data is noted below in italics, you can skip it unless you're nostalgic, like
me:</p>
